{"tid":1960114,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"諗下點解台灣當紅藝人會去對岸賺錢 但喺本土仲咁受歡迎？","createTime":"2020-04-06T02:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T09:18:39.000Z","uid":69891,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ba4af53f480f4da86f938569e415ab56512316","tid":1960114,"uid":69891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:36:28.000Z","msg":"第一，因為民眾對佢哋期望嘅係才華，係作品，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係政見</span><br />\n或者只要有好作品，安份守己就合格<br />\n<br />\n第二，因為佢哋明白要保住台灣文化市場，努力爭取更多觀眾同資源，同時保住台灣品牌同影響力<br />\n<br />\n蔡依林周杰倫蔡健雅蕭敬騰徐佳瑩你諗下有邊個冇賺過對岸錢<br />\n但又繼續喺台灣大紅大紫？<br />\n<br />\n而家香港得啲奀星仲要日日玩批鬥<br />\n仲邊會建立到影響力<br />\n借鏡一下台灣 <br />\n希望香港粵語嘅文化創作可以再度興盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287c81394c6288ad82e1c6451b00ce15d0f1cfac","tid":1960114,"uid":1654,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"吳宗憲黑人范范大小ass 比台灣人屌到捐返入老母閪你唔講？"},{"pid":"735d5746df572b1c78582515621b525618c801cb","tid":1960114,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">天真就係罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"757b4ea15d0d9988dd6be9289b2532d82d7eaebb","tid":1960114,"uid":69891,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"287c81394c6288ad82e1c6451b00ce15d0f1cfac","tid":1960114,"uid":1654,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"吳宗憲黑人范范大小ass 比台灣人屌到捐返入老母閪你唔講？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"呢D咪冇守本份囉<br />\n<br />\n更顯得台灣人識分應該鬥邊個<br />\n唔係不思考一過岸就鬥死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa60fefafc0df8d1f10bf0a566d8a914f52b6db","tid":1960114,"uid":28831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"757b4ea15d0d9988dd6be9289b2532d82d7e